Class Program

  org.mythdroid.data.Program
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Program>
public class Program
extends Object
implements Comparable<Program>

A Program - can be constructed from a stringlist (from a backend) or from XML (e.g. in Status or in the Guide).
